divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking pictures of baloon .I made approx. 4-6 pictures in 5 minutes and did not see anything strange. Later when i was showing pictures to my friend i saw in one picture appears strange object .Everyone says its airplane or something else .But there was no airplane ,no bird ,no other baloons!
